&lt;h2 id="architecture">Architecture&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>KRE is designed based on a microservice pattern to be run on top of a Kubernetes cluster.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>In the following diagram is described the main components and the relationship each other.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src=".github/images/kre-architecture.jpg" alt="Architecture">&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Below are described the main concepts of KRE.&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="krt">KRT&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>Konstellation Runtime Transport is a compressed file with the definition of a runtime version, included the code to
run and a YAML file called &lt;code>kre.yaml&lt;/code> with the desired workflows definitions.&lt;/p>
